<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chroma Estudio | Enlaces</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fbe39d; /* TU COLOR CREMA */
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            color: #8c641e; /* TU COLOR DORADO OSCURO */
        }
        .container { width: 100%; max-width: 400px; text-align: center; }
        
        .logo-img { 
            width: 110px; 
            height: auto; 
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            /* Si tu logo es oscuro, resaltará perfecto sobre el crema */
        }

        h1 { 
            font-size: 22px; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            letter-spacing: 3px; 
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #8c641e;
        }

        .insta-link {
            color: #8c641e;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .subtitle { 
            font-size: 15px; 
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #8c641e; 
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .link-button {
            display: block;
            background-color: #8c641e; /* BOTÓN DORADO */
            color: #fbe39d; /* LETRAS CREMA */
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid #8c641e;
        }

        .link-button:hover {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #8c641e;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .footer { 
            margin-top: 60px; 
            font-size: 10px; 
            color: #8c641e; 
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="Chroma Estudio" class="logo-img">
        
        <h1>CHROMA ESTUDIO</h1>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/chromaestudio" target="_blank" class="insta-link">@chromaestudio</a>
        <p class="subtitle">Diseño estratégico para tu negocio</p>

        <a href="https://wa.me/543512048953?text=Hola%20Chroma%20Estudio,%20me%20gustaría%20consultar%20por%20sus%20servicios" target="_blank" class="link-button">
            Contact us via WhatsApp
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://www.behance.net/rociomeyerr" target="_blank" class="link-button">
            Our work & Portfolio
        </a>

        <a href="https://forms.gle/hyitx4hqmV1oVpJP9" target="_blank" class="link-button">
            Formulario de contacto
        </a>

        <div class="footer">© 2026 CHROMA ESTUDIO</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
